---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import type { AboutProps, HeroProps } from "../types";
import Section from "./Section.astro";

type Props = AboutProps & Pick<HeroProps, "name">;

const { image, name } = Astro.props;
---

<Section text="About Me" textEs="Sobre mí" href="about">
  <!-- Cabecera de perfil: intro + foto -->
  <div class="grid items-center gap-8 md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_280px] lg:gap-12">
    <div class="about-description flex flex-col gap-6">
      <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
        ¡Hola! Soy Gustavo Luna 👋
      </h3>
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-balance">
        Soy un <span
          class="font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-950/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded"
          >desarrollador Full-Stack JavaScript</span
        > de 24 años, resido en <span
          class="font-semibold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300">Querétaro, México</span
        >. Acabo de egresar de <span class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200"
          >Ingeniería en Sistemas Computacionales</span
        > (UVEG, promedio 9.0), y hoy enfoco mi energía en la programación y la
        <span class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200"
          >inteligencia artificial</span
        >.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 text-base">
        <span class="text-slate-400">🌐</span>
        <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Idiomas:</span>
        <span
          class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-white bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
          >Español (Nativo)</span
        >
        <span
          class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-white bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
          >Inglés (B2)</span
        >
        <span
          class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-white bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
          >Francés (A2)</span
        >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-photo relative mx-auto h-80 w-64 shrink-0">
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-500/10 dark:bg-blue-500/20 blur-2xl rounded-lg"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="relative rotate-[5deg] bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-slate-100 p-4 md:rotate-[6deg] shadow-2xl"
      >
        <Image
          class="object-cover border-4 border-slate-200 shadow-xl"
          src={image}
          width="260"
          height="260"
          alt={name}
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Tarjetas de detalle -->
  <div class="mt-12 grid items-start gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
    <div
      class="bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 rounded-lg p-5 md:p-6"
    >
      <h4
        class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2"
      >
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path
            d="M10.394 2.08a1 1 0 00-.788 0l-7 3a1 1 0 000 1.84L5.25 8.051a.999.999 0 01.356-.257l4-1.714a1 1 0 11.788 1.838L7.667 9.088l1.94.831a1 1 0 00.787 0l7-3a1 1 0 000-1.838l-7-3zM3.31 9.397L5 10.12v4.102a8.969 8.969 0 00-1.05-.174 1 1 0 01-.89-.89 11.115 11.115 0 01.25-3.762zM9.3 16.573A9.026 9.026 0 007 14.935v-3.957l1.818.78a3 3 0 002.364 0l5.508-2.361a11.026 11.026 0 01.25 3.762 1 1 0 01-.89.89 8.968 8.968 0 00-5.35 2.524 1 1 0 01-1.4 0zM6 18a1 1 0 001-1v-2.065a8.935 8.935 0 00-2-.712V17a1 1 0 001 1z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        Certificaciones
      </h4>
      <ul class="space-y-2.5">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400 mt-1">▪</span>
          <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-medium"
            >Intermediate SQL — DataCamp</span
          >
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400 mt-1">▪</span>
          <a
            href="https://learn.mongodb.com/c/UhARMgERRzyn7bMzcpO_Zw"
            target="_blank"
            class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-300 hover:text-blue-500 dark:hover:text-blue-200 underline-offset-2 hover:underline font-medium transition-colors"
            >MongoDB Node.js Developer Path</a
          >
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400 mt-1">▪</span>
          <a
            href="https://www.credly.com/badges/f8049746-611a-4b20-8310-fe3a6c0f9168/public_url"
            target="_blank"
            class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-300 hover:text-blue-500 dark:hover:text-blue-200 underline-offset-2 hover:underline font-medium transition-colors"
            >Advanced Schema Design</a
          >
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400 mt-1">▪</span>
          <a
            href="https://www.credly.com/badges/01317c41-b90c-4362-9206-78c357ff36df/public_url"
            target="_blank"
            class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-300 hover:text-blue-500 dark:hover:text-blue-200 underline-offset-2 hover:underline font-medium transition-colors"
            >GitHub Foundations</a
          >
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400 mt-1">▪</span>
          <a
            href="https://www.credly.com/badges/7709c02c-2a2c-428e-825b-655874a86f41/public_url"
            target="_blank"
            class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-300 hover:text-blue-500 dark:hover:text-blue-200 underline-offset-2 hover:underline font-medium transition-colors"
            >AWS Cloud Practitioner</a
          >
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div
      class="bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 rounded-lg p-5 md:p-6"
    >
      <h4
        class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2"
      >
        <svg
          class="w-5 h-5"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        IA & Áreas de Interés
      </h4>
      <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-4">
        Trabajo en la intersección entre el <span
          class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200"
          >desarrollo full-stack y la IA</span
        >, integrando modelos e inteligencia en productos completos, de extremo a
        extremo.
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-2.5">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          <span class="text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400 mt-1">▪</span>
          <span><span class="font-semibold">RAG</span> con embeddings</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          <span class="text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400 mt-1">▪</span>
          <span>Servidores <span class="font-semibold">MCP</span> propios</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          <span class="text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400 mt-1">▪</span>
          <span>Entrenamiento y <span class="font-semibold">ajuste de modelos</span></span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          <span class="text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400 mt-1">▪</span>
          <span>Orquestación de <span class="font-semibold">agentes con LLMs</span></span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p
    class="mt-8 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed font-semibold text-green-700 dark:text-green-400 bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-950/30 border border-green-200 dark:border-green-900/50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center"
  >
    ✨ ¡Listo para nuevos desafíos y crear soluciones increíbles!
  </p>
</Section>
